{"tid":1568303,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影垃圾角色選舉","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:13:56.000Z","uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a0f3095ed0b37ad3d234aa39eebaa52b66f473","tid":1568303,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"火滾撚樣垃圾角色<br />\n1. 鳴狗 天真白癡 不學無術 淨係識影分身螺旋丸打嘴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.mk佐 忘恩負義 小櫻同香麟都想殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.港女櫻 臭雞一隻唔多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.鼬 動漫無咩野 但遊戲太難用 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.水門 害死老婆同個仔 自己學生又救唔撚到 但又輕輕浮浮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有血有肉好角色<br />\n1.帶土 為左條女改變世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.卡卡西 身邊重視嘅人都死晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咁fail 啲無合作精神嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.凱 努力型天才 最後犧牲自己打到斑仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.斑 殺伐果斷 唔會晒口水廢up <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76aef1a62adb60483b6b099ee85a52c344e367da","tid":1568303,"uid":123175,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾團助"},{"pid":"2cb711b7960711b0e1dd7304ac218b7ca7ea23af","tid":1568303,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76aef1a62adb60483b6b099ee85a52c344e367da","tid":1568303,"uid":123175,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾團助"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:14:41.0